      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "1 Kings 7:40 introduces the recapitulation of all the vessels made by Hiram. יהוה בּית, in the house of the Lord (cf. Ewald, 300, b.); in 2 Chronicles 4:11 more clearly, יי בּבית; we find it also in 1 Kings 7:45, for which we have in 2 Chronicles 4:16 יהוה לבית, for the house of Jehovah. The several objects enumerated in 1 Kings 7:41-45 are accusatives governed by לעשׂות.",
        "children": [
